16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 57 O.S. 2021, Section 332.1, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 332.1. A. The Pardon and Parole Board created by
19 Article VI, Section 10, of the Oklahoma Constitution is authorized
20 to employ professional investigators and such clerical and
21 administrative personnel as may be required to carry out the duties
22 and responsibilities under the provisions of this act.
23 B. The Pardon and Parole Board shall be authorized to employ
24 alternate members to serve on the Board.
